dct_title_s: Cave location map: Base map atlas sheet no. 40
dct_description_sm: The Cave Location Map lists 142 caves in the following counties: Hunterdon, Morris, Somerset, Sussex, and Warren. It features locations of Precambrian Franklin Marble, Cambro Ordovician Kittatinny Limestones, Ordovician Jacksonburg Formations, and Silurian-Devonian Limestones.
